<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="8" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="9.[192,1442,507,737]" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,303,507,533]" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Remarks.</emphasis>
The genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Darlington" authorityYear="1952" box="[435,564,508,533]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Notagonum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[435,564,508,533]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Notagonum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is known from 
<collectingCountry box="[746,859,507,533]" name="Indonesia" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Indonesia</collectingCountry>
, New 
<collectingCountry box="[930,1014,507,533]" name="Guinea-Bissau" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Guinea</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1027,1066,507,533]" name="Fiji" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Fiji</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1078,1155,507,533]" name="Samoa" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Samoa</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1167,1344,507,534]" name="New Caledonia" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">New Caledonia</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry name="Australia" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Australia</collectingCountry>
(including 
<collectingRegion box="[352,464,541,568]" country="Australia" name="Tasmania" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Tasmania</collectingRegion>
), 
<collectingCountry box="[484,650,541,567]" name="Norfolk Island" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Norfolk Island</collectingCountry>
, Lord Howe Island, and 
<collectingCountry box="[933,1084,541,568]" name="New Zealand" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">New Zealand</collectingCountry>
where it is represented by four endemic species occurring on the North Island, South Island, Stewart Island, and two offshore islands (TH, 
<collectingCountry box="[1386,1430,575,601]" name="Switzerland" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">CH</collectingCountry>
). 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Darlington" authorityYear="1952" box="[192,321,610,635]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Notagonum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[192,321,610,635]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Notagonum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Darlington seems to be a genus of convenience or a paraphyletic taxon (
<bibRefCitation author="Darlington PJ" box="[1143,1332,609,636]" pageId="9" pageNumber="8" pagination="89 - 252" refId="ref55121" refString="Darlington PJ Jr. 1952. The carabid beetles of New Guinea. Part 2. The Agonini. Bulletin of the Museum of Comparative Zoology 107: 89 - 252." type="journal article" year="1952">Darlington 1952</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Liebherr JK" pageId="9" pageNumber="8" pagination="263 - 295" refId="ref55829" refString="Liebherr JK. 2005. Platynini (Coleoptera: Carabidae) of Vanuatu: Miocene diversification on the Melanesian Arc. Invertebrate Systematics 19: 263 - 295." type="journal article" year="2005">Liebherr 2005</bibRefCitation>
). 
<taxonomicName authority="(Erichson, 1842)" baseAuthorityName="Erichson" baseAuthorityYear="1842" box="[271,747,643,669]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Notagonum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="marginellum">
<emphasis box="[271,549,643,669]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Notagonum marginellum</emphasis>
(Erichson, 1842)
</taxonomicName>
was deleted from the 
<collectingCountry box="[1005,1156,643,670]" name="New Zealand" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">New Zealand</collectingCountry>
fauna by 
<bibRefCitation author="Larochelle A &amp; Lariviere M-C." pageId="9" pageNumber="8" pagination="1 - 188" refId="ref55629" refString="Larochelle A, Lariviere M-C. 2007. Carabidae (Insecta: Coleoptera): synopsis of supraspecific taxa. Fauna of New Zealand 60: 1 - 188." type="journal article" year="2007">Larochelle and Larivière (2007: 81)</bibRefCitation>
; this species occurs in 
<collectingRegion box="[682,792,677,703]" country="Australia" name="Tasmania" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Tasmania</collectingRegion>
, southern mainland 
<collectingCountry box="[1029,1133,677,703]" name="Australia" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Australia</collectingCountry>
, and on Lord Howe Island (
<bibRefCitation author="Baehr M." box="[199,354,711,737]" pageId="9" pageNumber="8" pagination="1 - 24" refId="ref54109" refString="Baehr M. 2016. The Notagonum marginellum-submetallicum- complex with description of new genera and species of Platynini from Australia (Insecta, Coleoptera, Carabidae, Platynini). Entomologische Blatter und Coleoptera 112: 1 - 24." type="journal article" year="2016">Baehr 2016: 1</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
